---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
import { SITE } from "../site-config";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-4" title="关于我">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="sr-only">
      你好，我是 {SITE.author.firstName}，一名来自 China Mainland 的废物萌新。
    </p>
    <div aria-hidden="true" class="text-sm font-light">
      <p class="text-sm font-light">
        你好，我是 {SITE.author.firstName}，
        一名来自 China Mainland 的废物萌新。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 技能栈精简展示 -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-1">
      <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-darkslate-400/60 text-darkslate-200 border border-darkslate-400/30">Flutter</span>
      <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-darkslate-400/60 text-darkslate-200 border border-darkslate-400/30">Dart</span>
      <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-darkslate-400/60 text-darkslate-200 border border-darkslate-400/30">Python</span>
      <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-darkslate-400/60 text-darkslate-200 border border-darkslate-400/30">VSCode</span>
      <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-darkslate-400/60 text-darkslate-200 border border-darkslate-400/30">Vue</span>
      <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-darkslate-400/60 text-darkslate-200 border border-darkslate-400/30">Minecraft</span>
    </div>

    <!-- 爱好与个人兴趣 -->
    <p class="text-xs font-light text-darkslate-300 mt-1">
      除此以外还热衷：设计、插画、动画、3D 建模、旅行 & ACG 🎮
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
